My name is Chad and I am the owner of Blast Your Bins - Pressure Washing Service.  I have been helping homeowners and farmers with all of their cleaning needs since 2020.  We can clean your gutters, siding, deck, concrete pads, fence, windows and farming equipment for one low price.  

Our water supply is 100% self contained, meaning we do NOT need to connect to your water supply.  We can clean your equipment even if it's out in the middle of a field!

We service Southern Alberta including Lethbridge, Pincher Creek, Nanton, Bow Island and more.  Call us today for more information - 403 892 4703
